Affiliation = {Mekheimer, KS (Corresponding Author), Al Azhar Univ, Fac Sci, Dept Math, Cairo 11884, Egypt.
   Mekheimer, Khaled Saad; El-Sayed, Mohamed Obeid Mohamed; Gouda, Ashraf A., Al Azhar Univ, Fac Sci, Dept Math, Nasr City, Cairo, Egypt.
