Affiliation = {Zhao, Y (Corresponding Author), Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Comp Technol, Beijing 100190, Peoples R China.
   Li, JP (Corresponding Author), South China Univ Technol, Sch Automat Sci \& Technol, Guangzhou 510640, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Sheng; Zhao, Fangyuan; Bu, Dechao; Zhao, Yi, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Comp Technol, Beijing 100190, Peoples R China.
